      "span_text": "Recently, HBV DNA assays that utilize real-time PCR technology with improved sensitivity (5-10 IU/mL) and wider dynamic range (up to 8-9 log 10 IU/mL) have become available. Quantification of serum HBV DNA is a crucial component in the evaluation of patients with chronic HBV infection and in the assessment of the efficacy of antiviral treatment."
